com.bmc.arsys.apitransport.session

Interface RpcMapperI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RpcMapperV14, RpcMapperV15, RpcMapperV16, RpcMapperV17, RpcMapperV18, RpcMapperV19, RpcMapperV20, RpcMapperV21, RpcMapperV22

    public interface RpcMapperI
    Interface for the Rpc version mapping class between version v(X+1) and version vX Every rpc version mapping class from a API program needs to implement this interface for the call back on the rpc version down grade works Other lower version mapping classes should extends the version above i.e in api.session package: class RpcMapperVx implements RpcMapperI CMDB needs to provide it's Rpc version mapper for each Rpc version it supports class RpcMapperVx implements RpcMapperI
